Create a new GtfsFeed

Parameters:
agency_name - the human-readable agency name
agency_url - the agency's location on the WWW
country - The country where this agency is located
data_exchange_id - The ID of this feed on GTFS Data Exchange
data_exchange_url - The URL of this feed's page on GTFS Data Exchange
date_added - The date this was added to this site or to GTFS Data Exchange, whichever is earlier. Defaults to today.
date_updated - The date this feed was last updated on this site
feed_base_url - The URL where this feed may be found on the WWW. May be a direct URL or a developer site.
license_url - The URL where the license of this feed can be found
official - Is this feed provided and supported by the respective agency
state - The US state abbreviation of this feed
area_description - The human readable description of the area where this feed is located
geometry - The EWKT geometry of the bounds of this feed
